arts.ttl: Inter Milan Captain Fighting Atletico Madrid Star For Place In Argentina Starting XI Vs Venezuela
arts.sum: Inter Milan captain Lautaro Martinez is in contention for the starting line-up in the upcoming World Cup qualifier between Argentina and Venezuela. According to TyC Sports via FCInterNews, El Toro faces competition from Atletico Madrid forward Thiago Almada. Despite already securing a place in next summer’s tournament, Argentina will look to build momentum.
